        <p style="color:#00253b; font-size:1rem; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">"What's our return policy for items bought during a sale?"</p>
        <div role="tabpanel" id="cad-panel-generic" aria-labelledby="cad-tab-generic" data-cad-panel="generic">
          <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.9375rem; line-height:1.8;">"Return policies vary by retailer. Most stores allow returns within 30 days of purchase, though sale items are sometimes excluded. Please check with the specific store for their exact policy."</p>
        </div>
